data.col_1: How to place bids using the Bid Sheet

data.col_2: Step 1: Click on the "Bid Sheet" tab.
Step 2: Ensure that all cells in the "Complete Bid" column either show "Yes" or are blank (meaning that you do not intend to bid on that lot).
Step 3: Enter bids for each lot that you wish to be awarded.
Step 4: Upload the completed file using your browser.
Yellow cells can be populated by you. Columns with an asterisk (*) are mandatory.
If you wish to be awarded a lot, you must at a minimum complete all related mandatory cells.
Do not make changes to any other areas within the spreadsheet. Doing so may prevent the processing of the completed Bid Sheet.
Only the Excel .xlsx format can be accepted and processed.
Feedback cells are only visible if feedback has been enabled for this event. Feedback cells cannot be populated by you.
Any visible feedback refers to Round 2.
